{"word":"στροβέω","slug":"στροβέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στροβέω</b></el> <el>(στροβέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στρόβος'><el>στρόβος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to twist, twirl</i> or <i>whirl about</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to make dizzy, distract</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to whirl about</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}